avocados
avocados %>% 
  distinct(region)
avocados_tidy <- avocados %>% 
  mutate(month = month(Date))
  
avocados_tidy <- avocados_tidy %>% 
  mutate(season = case_when(between(month, 3, 5) ~ "Spring",
                            between(month, 6, 8) ~ "Summer",
                            between(month, 9, 11) ~ "Fall",
                            between(month, 1, 2) ~ "Winter",
                            TRUE ~ "Winter"
                            )
         )
